{"tid":1338311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（持久戰）以後可以每個禮拜去西環","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:47:25.000Z","uid":120623,"like":114,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b863a89865abfbe516935faa6d9c0f2547bb203f","tid":1338311,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"（冷靜啲）大家得返兩三日機會，不妨諗下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1255454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1255454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（緊急）如果現場人士識突發轉場就世界級<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259576</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家係時候對準中聯辦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1314644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1314644</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解遲早都要去西環？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n去西環，只係遲早既事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329958</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n經過今日，內心真係好激動<br />\n由六月講到宜家，本身諗住728先會發生既事<br />\n今日終於發生咗，事實亦證明呢個方向係啱<br />\n可以諗下討論下點樣打持久戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9ff41538bfa055d77f7c2ac8ba8b1e44d0a245","tid":1338311,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"大家加油"},{"pid":"c8f4f54cd3886223abe1f38bb622fc0b610d2239","tid":1338311,"uid":212182,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"劍指中央咽喉！"},{"pid":"5d4b441faa02b2d9bce76f4c813daa6b43c577c3","tid":1338311,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9ff41538bfa055d77f7c2ac8ba8b1e44d0a245","tid":1338311,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"大家加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img 