面達6,748方呎，2016年12月30日斥資1.2152億元購入<br />\n寶翠園2座26樓D室，2018年9月19日斥資1,720萬元購入，實用面積664方呎，呎價25,904元<br />\n觀塘凱滙3及5座43至49樓合共20伙，總樓面11,762方呎，2019年2月斥資2.47532億元購入<br />\n<br />\n截至2019年4月政府披露的立法會財委會文件顯示過去5個財政年度，中聯辦和中央機構共獲豁免1.28億元印花稅。//"},{"pid":"45618c625f8e279626664a105f3eb623fbe7e3ec","tid":1338311,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔建議 下次警方應該有部署 有無第二啲指標性啲既野"},{"pid":"9606401a355b54c8ceee41a7f0c0a87482d860b8","tid":1338311,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"1早講咗"},{"pid":"627a675776b55811e3100a3051dbe4849cf0bf30","tid":1338311,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45618c625f8e279626664a105f3eb623fbe7e3ec","tid":1338311,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔建議 下次警方應該有部署 有無第二啲指標性啲既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"上面，中聯辦其他物業，真正be water"},{"pid":"c69604a7ba811111beef74b433b7223a9fc2dbb9","tid":1338311,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9606401a355b54c8ceee41a7f0c0a87482d860b8","tid":1338311,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"1早講咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"又見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a6b026790cf259d1bccfa2ecbfa4a45a6266b9","tid":1338311,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本冇得估 <br />\n分分鐘唔係呢區"},{"pid":"51f28fd0ba0912bf4f2915b46ab1ea87dca62326","tid":1338311,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a6b026790cf259d1bccfa2ecbfa4a45a6266b9","tid":1338311,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 